          Across Germany, Switzerland, Austria, the UK, and Ireland, employers have a duty of care for every employee — including those working from home. A properly structured wellbeing programme naturally produces the documentation that satisfies those obligations. You do not need to choose between caring for your people and meeting your legal duties. Done properly, they are the same thing.
